00:22:13.030 --> 00:22:14.520
it's the identity matrix.

00:22:14.520 --> 00:22:17.278
In component
notation, we're going

00:22:17.278 --> 00:22:18.570
to call it the Kronecker delta.

00:22:48.710 --> 00:22:51.170
Just as little
aside, if I started

00:22:51.170 --> 00:22:54.260
with the barred on the
left side and the unbarred

00:22:54.260 --> 00:22:57.020
in the right-hand side and
